STEP2：語句一致判定】\n※部分マッチ可\n※下記語句**いずれか1つ以上を入力に含む**場合に該当（表記ゆれ・類義語の勝手な追加は禁止、リスト記載のものに限る）\n※自然言語の助詞・接続詞・敬語（「です」「ます」「ね」「お願いします」「と思います」 等）が前後にあっても判定する\n※複数のラベルがマッチした場合は上から優先（家族側のキーワードが含まれる場合は、はい等の肯定語が同時に含まれていても家族優先で判定する。家族の方が情報量が多く、誤判定リスクが低いため評価順を厳守）\n\n---\n\n### 家族\n- 家族\n- 親\n- 妻\n- 夫\n- 息子\n- 娘\n- 母\n- 父\n- いいえ\n- 違います\n\n→ 家族\n\n### 本人\n- はい\n- そうです\n- はい本人です\n- 本人\n- 私\n- 私です\n- 自分\n- 大丈夫\n\n→ 本人\n\n---\n\n## 【STEP3：それ以外】\n以下は NO_RESULT：\n\n- 無音\n- フィラーのみ（例：えー あのー のみ）\n- 意味不明\n- 上記いずれのキーワードにもマッチしない入力","functionCall":"","promptTTS":"","contextName":"callerSubject","contextDisplayType":"CLASSIFICATION","addCurrentDate":"No"}},"save-firstVisit":{"layout":{"x":840,"y":3900},"next":[],"subs":[{"moduleName":"","label":""},{"moduleName":"","label":""},{"moduleName":"","label":""}],"name":"save-firstVisit","description":"","matchingmethod":1,"type":"drjoy^Persistence$save2db","params":{"contextName":"firstVisit","contextDisplayType":"CLASSIFICATION"}},"当院受診確認":{"layout":{"x":560,"y":3900},"next":[{"condition":"^.*$","label":"Next Module","nextModuleName":"入力_当院受診確認"}],"subs":[{"moduleName":"save-firstVisit","label":"save-firstVisit"},{"moduleName":"","label":""},{"moduleName":"","label":""}],"name":"当院受診確認","description":"","matchingmethod":1,"type":"drjoy^Text To Speech$Text to speech","params":{"prompt":"","stop_by_dtmf":"No","category_words":""}},"入力_当院受診確認":{"layout":{"x":560,"y":4050},"next":[{"condition":"^TIMEOUT$","label":"timeout","nextModuleName":"リトライ_当院受診確認"},{"condition":"^ERROR$","label":"error","nextModuleName":"リトライ_当院受診確認"},{"condition":"^NO_RESULT$","label":"no_result","nextModuleName":"リトライ_当院受診確認"},{"condition":"^.+$","label":"success","nextModuleName":"OpenAI_当院受診確認"},{"condition":"","label":"","nextModuleName":""},{"condition":"","label":"","nextModuleName":""},{"condition":"","label":"","nextModuleName":""},{"condition":"","label":"","nextModuleName":""},{"condition":"","label":"","nextModuleName":""},{"condition":"","label":"","nextModuleName":""},{"co